<h5 id="subject_1129291">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=127222.msg1129291#msg1129291" rel="nofollow">Re: 【DW12th】神秘博士TRPG 第三章：我能对抗怪物，但不能对抗物理</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1129291'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1129291'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #7 于:</strong> 2021-08-13, 周五 15:19:26 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1129291_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1129291"><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size">CONFLICT: CONTESTED ROLLS<br>冲突：对抗掷骰</span></span></strong><br><br>掷骰把数字加起来，与设定的难度值比较，这固然很好，但你如果是要积极地反抗该怎么办？幸运的是，这和普通任务一样简单，只是难度值是由对手决定的，因为他们会试图阻止你做任何事情。<br><br>大多数时候，冲突产生于玩家控制的角色和游戏主持人控制的对手之间，所以主持人要声明反派们的行动，并代替他们掷骰——这就是角色们要努力超过的数值，就像普通任务的难度值一样。实际上，是反派制造麻烦试图打败角色这件事设置了玩家掷骰的难度值。<br><br>如果这听起来很难，别担心，我们会带你逐步了解这一机制。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Rolling dice and adding some numbers together to beat a set Difficulty is all well and good, but what if you’re actively opposing someone or something else? Luckily, this is just as easy as a normal task, only the Difficulty is determined by the opponent as they try to stop whatever you’re doing.<br><br>Most of the time, Conflicts are between the players’ characters and antagonists controlled by the Gamemaster, so the Gamemaster will state what the bad guys are trying to do and make a roll on behalf of them first – this will be what the characters will have to try to beat, just like the Difficulty of a normal task. In effect, they are setting the Difficulty of the player’s roll by making things difficult to succeed against them.<br><br>Don’t worry if this sounds confusing, we’ll take you through how it works stage by stage.</div></div></div><br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>INTENT<br>意图</strong></span></span><br>&nbsp;<br>这部分和以前一样。玩家描述自己想做什么，而主持人决定NPC要怎么阻止——突袭、开火、躲避等等。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">This works just as before. The player says what they want to do, and the Gamemaster determines what the Non-Player Character is doing to prevent it – looming to attack, opening fire, dodging, and so on.</div></div></div><br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>WHAT ARE YOU USING?<br>你要用什么技能？</strong></span></span><br><br>接下来，看看使用什么属性+技能来达成目标，以及是否有相关的特性。双方根据计划好的行动确定掷骰方案。掷骰方式就和其他任何任务一样。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Next, see which Attribute + Skill you’re using to do what you’re intending, and if any traits are relevant. Both sides work out what they need to roll, relating to their planned action. This is done in just the same way as any other task.</div></div></div><br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>ROLL THE DICE<br>掷骰</strong></span></span><br><br>像之前一样，游戏主持人将属性+技能（以及任何有关的特性）数值与掷骰点数加起来，来决定对手的表现。玩家同样如此做，并将结果告知主持人。主持人使用对手的结果作为玩家掷骰的难度值，计算玩家是否成功。如果玩家失败，则反派占上风，对手采取行动。如果玩家成功，则他们得以按预期行动，并与主持人在剧情进展上达成一致。<br><br>这就是冲突机制。从打斗到争论，每件事都以完全相同的方式判定。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Just as before, the Gamemaster adds the Attribute + Skill (as well as taking any traits into account) to the dice roll, determining how well the antagonists do. The player does the same and informs the Gamemaster what the result is. The Gamemaster uses the antagonist’s result as the Difficulty for the player’s rolls, and works out if the player is successful or not. If the player fails, then evil prevails and the antagonists take their action. If the player succeeds, their intended actions go ahead – and they agree with the Gamemaster what exactly happened.<br><br>This is how it is done for any Conflict, from fighting to arguing, everything works in exactly the same way.</div></div></div><br><strong>示例：</strong>克拉拉和博士正在探索一栋传言闹鬼的大楼；一如经典的恐怖片风格，他们分头行动了。克拉拉调查了地下室里奇怪的砰砰声，发现了鬼魂出没的原因——那里有许多棺材，里面全是由超凡智慧控制的低语者！她想悄悄撤退，却被身后凭空出现的低语者发现了！游戏主持人彼得问扮演克拉拉的玩家塞缪尔，克拉拉要怎么做。<br><br>塞缪尔知道博士就在楼上，如果克拉拉拖住那个低语者足够久，博士就能来救她。塞缪尔决定尝试说服低语者不要进攻——它的主人可能更想活捉克拉拉。彼得认为这很合理，并说低语者打算抓住克拉拉让她心跳停止。<br><br>塞缪尔查他的角色卡，彼得则查找低语者的属性和技能。两人都把必要的属性和技能相加计算——对克拉拉而言，她需要骰<em>气质</em>+<em>说服</em>来劝低语者放她一条生路。<br><br>彼得查了低语者的<em>协调</em>+<em>斗殴</em>技能决定怎么骰。尽管低语者可能被说服，但在没有阻碍的情况下，它仍会使用必要的属性+技能。<br><br>低语者逼近了，克拉拉试图阻止它杀死自己。塞缪尔和彼得都掷骰，将各自的属性和技能相加，并将相关特性特性计算在内。塞缪尔骰出的结果更高，但也只是刚刚好。塞缪尔决定冲突的结果，他选择让低语者不攻击。然而，结果只是一个“是的，但是”，所以塞缪尔决定，低语者抓住了克拉拉，准备把她交给非凡智慧。克拉拉还活着，但被俘虏了！她需要寻找下一个逃跑的机会。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><em><strong>Example:</strong> Clara and the Doctor are exploring a strange mansion, rumoured to be haunted; in true horror-movie style, they split up. Investigating the strange banging in the basement, Clara finds the cause of the haunting – there are coffins full of Whisper Men, controlled by the Great Intelligence! She tries to back quietly out but is spotted by a Whisper Man who has just appeared out of thin air behind her! The Gamemaster, Peter, asks Clara’s player, Samuel, what Clara is going to do.<br><br>Samuel knows that the Doctor is upstairs and will be able to rescue her if she can delay the Whisper Man long enough. Samuel decides to attempt to persuade the Whisper Man to stop it from attacking, to tell it that its master might prefer her alive. Peter thinks this sounds good, and says the Whisper Man is intending to seize Clara and stop her heart.<br><br>Samuel checks his character sheet, and Peter looks up the Whisper Man’s attributes and skills. They add the necessary attributes and skills together – in Clara’s case it will be her Presence + Convince to tell the Whisper Man to let her live.<br><br>Peter looks up the Whisper Man’s Coordination + Fighting skills to see what he needs to roll. Even though it may be talked down, the Whisper Man still uses the Attribute + Skill it would use if it had no resistance.<br><br>The Whisper Man looms, and Clara tries to stop it from killing her. Both Samuel and Peter roll their dice, and add their respective attribute and skills, taking into account any traits. Samuel has a higher result, but only just. Samuel decides the outcome of the conflict and determines that the Whisper Man doesn’t attack. However, the result was only a “Yes, But” so Samuel decides that the Whisper Man takes Clara prisoner to take to the Great Intelligence. She’s alive, but held captive! She needs to keep an eye out for another opportunity to escape.</em></div></div></div><br><strong><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">COMPLICATIONS<br>复杂事件</span></span></strong><br><br>如果你想在冲突中加入更多现实情况或细节，可以考虑一些环境因素。如果当前的任务比较棘手，或者有下雨、黑暗、角色仓促行动等情况，游戏主持人可以查看以下示例，合理运用调整值。这只是个参考准则，玩家可以根据喜好自由修改掷骰点数。不过，只有谨慎使用这些修改，才会让游戏变得更加快速流畅。<br><br>当然，在冲突中只有一方受到影响时，才应该考虑使用调整值。如果两者受到同等的影响（例如，在全黑的房间里，双方都没有照明或夜视镜），你就不必担心这类事情。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">If you wish to add more realism or detail into a Conflict, certain environmental factors can be taken into account. If the task at hand is tricky or complicated, or there are conditions such as rain, darkness or the character is hurried, the Gamemaster can have a look at the examples provided below and apply a modifier that seems suitable. These are just a guideline, and Gamemasters should feel free to modify the rolls as they see fit, though it makes for a speedier and smoother game if these modifiers are used sparingly.<br><br>Of course, modifiers should be taken into account in a Conflict only if one side alone is affected by it. If both are affected equally (for example, the room is in complete darkness and neither side has a light or nightvision goggles), you don’t need to worry about this sort of thing.</div></div></div><br><span style="color: orange;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">复杂事件示例</span></strong></span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><table class="bbc_table"><tr><td>角色发动突袭；明显占优势；对手分心或被迷惑<td>+2</tr><tr><td>无影响因素，或所有人受同样的影响<td>+0</tr><tr><td>照明不良；略为仓促；目标在20米开外<td>-1</tr><tr><td>角色遭到突袭；一心二用；目标以奔跑速度移动<td>-2</tr><tr><td>照明恶劣（极暗，没有月光和路灯）且对手能夜视；受惊；一心三用；<br>射击目标的特定部位（头部，手部，轮子，等等）<td>-4</tr><tr><td>目标在200米开外或以高速行驶速度移动；一心四用<td>-6</tr><tr><td>在全黑环境中与能夜视的对手战斗；射击视线外的目标；<br>刚睡醒就被迫自卫<td>-10</tr></table><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/08/13/fDqEVg.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/></div></div></div><br><strong><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">MULTIPLE OPPONENTS<br>多个对手</span></span></strong><br><br>在冲突中，常常会有不止一个对手与角色们作对。主持人可以为对手使用合作规则（见76页）以保持游戏节奏，而不是为每个对手分开掷骰。<br><br>主持人选择一个敌人作为团队领袖，比如赛博人领袖或桑塔将军。领袖掷骰对抗角色们，每个有可用技能的“小兵”提供+2点数。在“远程”战斗中，人们互相射击，对单个目标射击次数的限制较少，因此在某些冲突中可以弃用四人增援的上限。当对手的队伍非常庞大时，这些调整值会让角色难以应对。任何角色都不应该试图在没有充分准备时就直面多个戴立克或桑塔人。<br><br>在大型冲突中，主持人可以将对手分成实力相近、易于操控的“小队”。在这种情况下，对手应该分成人数相同的组去袭击角色。例如，一群桑塔人与博士、克拉拉和丹尼对阵。一共有10个桑塔人，所以主持人将敌人分成三组，3个对付克拉拉，3个对付丹尼，还有4个对付博士。<br><br>每个小组有一个临时“领袖”（如果原先整个队伍没有的话）。这样的大规模冲突在<strong>《保卫地球：UNIT资料书》</strong>中有更详细的介绍。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Often in Conflicts, there will be more than one adversary actively opposing the characters. Instead of rolling for each individual opponent, the Gamemaster may use the Cooperation rules (see pg.76) for the adversaries to keep things running quickly.<br><br>The Gamemaster should choose one of the adversaries to function as the leader for the group, such as the Cyberleader or Sontaran General. The leader makes the main roll against the characters, gaining a +2 bonus to the roll for each of their ‘troops’ with the appropriate skill. In ‘ranged’ combat, where people are shooting at each other, there are fewer limitations to how many can shoot at a single target, so the four maximum may be disregarded in some conflicts. With very large groups of opponents, these modifiers make things very difficult for the characters. No character should try to face off against multiple Daleks or Sontarans without something serious up their sleeves.<br><br>For large conflicts, the Gamemaster can split the enemy forces into equal, manageable ‘chunks’. In such a case, the opponents should be split into an equal number of groups to the characters. For example, a whole squad of Sontarans faces off against the Doctor, Clara and Danny. The squad is 10 Sontarans, so the Gamemaster splits the enemy into three groups, 3 against Clara, 3 against Danny and 4 Sontarans against the Doctor.<br><br>Each group would be given a ‘leader’ temporarily (if there isn’t already a leader in the group as a whole). Larger scale conflicts like this are covered in more detail in <strong>Defending The Earth: The UNIT Sourcebook</strong>.</div></div></div><br><strong>示例：</strong>在宇宙飞船亚里士多德号上，博士和克拉拉赶在联合抵抗部队进攻戴立克前哨基地之前与上校摩根·布鲁交谈。博士必须说服上校停止进攻——那一定是个陷阱！布鲁上校的左膀右臂诺斯中尉，戴立克的秘密傀儡，则声称必须占领前哨基地！<br><br>博士尝试对布鲁上校使用<em>气质</em>+<em>说服</em>，而上校使用<em>决心</em>+<em>说服</em>进行反驳，认为联合抵抗部队必胜。博士非常健谈，能言善辩，但同时诺斯中尉也在对上校咬耳朵，警告他上次博士出现时，他们差点就丢了飞船、输掉战争！诺斯的说服技能也起了作用，为布鲁上校的掷骰增加了点数。<br><br>玩家们掷骰子，用布鲁上校的掷骰结果来确定博士的难度值。博士骰出了Failure——他没能说服布鲁上校停止进攻，<strong>但</strong>上校注意到了博士的警告——这可能是一个陷阱，并指示部队提高警惕。<br><br>博士或许失败了，但这还不是彻头彻尾的灾难。现在，他只要自己进入戴立克前哨站，试着挫败戴立克的计划就行了！<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><em><strong>Example:</strong> The Doctor and Clara are onboard the spaceship Aristotle, talking to Colonel Morgan Blue in advance of an attack by the Combined Army Resistance on a Dalek outpost. The Doctor has to convince the Colonel to call off the attack – it has to be a trap! Colonel Blue’s right-hand man, Lieutenant North, who is secretly a Dalek puppet, argues that the outpost must be seized!<br><br>The Doctor tries to use his Presence + Convince on Colonel Blue, and the Colonel uses his Resolve +Convince to argue back, determined that the Combined Army Resistance must prevail. The Doctor is a very talkative and persuasive person, but Colonel Blue also has Lieutenant North talking into his ear at the same time, warning him that the last time the Doctor appeared they nearly lost the ship – and the war! North’s Convince is called into play as well, adding to Colonel Blue’s roll.<br><br>Dice are rolled, using Colonel Blue’s result to determine the Difficulty for the Doctor’s roll. The Doctor gets a Failure – Colonel Blue isn’t going to be convinced not to launch the attack, BUT he heeds the Doctor’s warning that it might be a trap and instructs his troops to be on their guard.<br><br>The Doctor may have failed but it wasn’t a complete disaster. Now, he just needs to get into the Dalek outpost himself to try to foil whatever it is the Daleks have planned!</em></div></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
